data.description: Welcome to this stylish newly built home in the Southbrook Golf course community ready for its next owners. Once you enter the home you will notice the open design and the fresh modern look of todays colors and materials. Open concept and design of the main level provides easy use of the living dining and kitchen area. Seller has added a 16 X 20 off the dining room for your outdoor entertaining needs. The rear yard backs up to  Southbrook's community park so your green space feels much larger and  free use of the playground and basketball court without having to add one to your yard. Home offers 2 bedrooms on the upper level and 2 in the lower level. There is a full bath on each level along with a private bath in the primary bedroom. You will love the expansive space the lower level great room offers.  Excellent opportunity to own this beautiful home in the Southbrook golf course development.
